  "title": "Scientist Engineer - One North / R&D / ASAP",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Opportunity</strong></p><ul><li>Opportunity to work in R&D organisation</li><li>Seeking for Scientist</li><li>Monday to Friday, 8:30am to 6pm</li><li>Nearest MRT: One North</li><li>3 years contract (renewable/convertible)</li></ul><p><strong>The Talent</strong></p><ul><li>PhD in Physics, Electrical, Electronics, Mechanical, Mechatronic, Microelectronics or any related studies</li><li>Experience in optics/quantum information experiments</li><li>Experience with free space fiber or optics</li><li>Excellent experimental background in microwave measurements at cryogenic temperatures and VNA-based</li><li>Understand of optical modelling and data analysis skills</li><li>Candidates with or without experience are welcome to apply!</li></ul><p><strong>The Job</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain and operate optical setup for memory experiment</li><li>Responsible time-domain and frequency-domain experiments to investigate the performance</li><li>Perform optical measurement in cryogenic environment</li><li>Perform cryogenic microwave experiments toward microwave-to-optical transduction</li><li>Modify dilution refrigerator on microwave measurement platforms and RF components</li><li>Support the integration of microwave and optical experimental platforms for hybrid memory and transduction experiments</li></ul><p><strong>Next Step:</strong></p><ul><li>Simply click on 'Apply here' to drop your resume or email to <a href=\"mailto:edmond.lee@adecco.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">edmond.lee@adecco.com</a></li></ul><p><br />Edmond Lee</p><p>Direct Line: 8206 8857</p><p>EA License No: 91C2918</p><p>Personnel Registration Number: R23114813<a href=\"mailto:edmond.lee@adecco.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
